	   <tr><td colspan=2>LOL, no magic equations involved, there is a damage bonus table with increase in db as level increases and as delay increases. as you get 50+ the 2h db is +1 per level except at 55 and 60, where you get more (5 for a 49ish dly weapon, 4 for 30-40ish delay). 1hs db has nothing to do with dly at all, is 9 for everyone from the time it becomes 9 (I was too high for it to show the lower numbers when they started showing db on weapons, so don't know when it becomes 9), becomes 10 at 55, and 11 at 60 (I think, may be at 59).<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Abazagaroth Katzkortulu<br>Knight of The Rathe<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=42861" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=42861</a></td></tr>
